A curate is a vicar's assistant. He attends different sevices throughout the week like weddings, funerals, baptisms;and,visits certain people who are sick and have problems to talk over.
In a service he would wear a white surplice over a cassock which is a long flowing black robe. He has a clerical collar around his neck,which shows that he has turned away from the rest of the World,and is doing what God wants him to accomplish. The collar has a piece of white plastic going through it to show he is a vicar.
{Cont.}
